    "Our approach introduces additional computational costs due to multiple generations and/or paraphrasing, which may increase the latency of the output.",
    "The steps, however, can be parallelized to ensure O(1) complexity.",
    "This work quantifies and reduces uncertainty in LLM outputs.",
    "It may help to reduce the generation and use of mistaken or misleading content from LLMs, to encourage a safer use of these models.",
    "For GPT series, we sample temperature uniformly from 0.0 to 2.0, and for PaLM series, the range is restricted from 0.0 to 1.0 by the API."
